OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782199087
OL,3,CSpeed-loving OAP races round Thruxton
OL,4,Cat 130mph
OL,6,FAt 98, sports car enthusiast Patricia
OL,7,FElliott, didn't hesitate when offered
OL,8,Fthe opportunity to get back on the
OL,9,Frace track.
OL,11,FThe former British Aerospace employee,
OL,12,Fand Winchester care home resident,
OL,13,Frelived her love of fast cars -
OL,14,Freaching speeds of over 130mph in an
OL,15,FAston Martin at Thruxton Race Circuit.
OL,17,F"I don't think we even had 130mph on
OL,18,Fthe speedometer in my day." said Miss
OL,19,FElliott.
OL,26,@yD@AOUzD@[O]
