OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782199087
OL,3,CSpeed-loving OAP races round Thruxton
OL,4,Cat 130mph
OL,6,F"I've been around for quite a long
OL,7,Ftime now, but this is one of those
OL,8,Fmemories that will really stick with
OL,9,Fme. It's not something I'll ever
OL,10,Fforget."
OL,12,FSara Stagg, Resident Wellbeing Co-
OL,13,Fordinator at The Dower House said:
OL,14,F"She has always been a huge fan of
OL,15,Fsports cars, and when we asked if
OL,16,Fshe'd like to experience it again, she
OL,17,Fjumped at the chance."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@HO]vD@AOUyD@VO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
