OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782199087
OL,3,CSpeed-loving OAP races round Thruxton
OL,4,Cat 130mph
OL,6,FPatricia's cousin, Susan McLaren,
OL,7,Ftravelled from Scotland to see her
OL,8,Ftake on the track: "We couldn't
OL,9,Fbelieve our eyes when we received the
OL,10,Femail saying Patricia was thinking
OL,11,Fabout getting back into a racing car
OL,12,Fat the age of 98.
OL,14,F"It's quite something. But at the same
OL,15,Ftime, we weren't surprised at all.
OL,16,FIt's very Patricia."
OL,18,FPatricia Elliott was one of only two
OL,19,Fwomen working at British Aerospace
OL,20,Fnearly 70 years ago, where her passion
OL,21,Ffor cars first began.
OL,26,@pD@TOUxD@TO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
