OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782199087
OL,3,CSpeed-loving OAP races round Thruxton
OL,4,Cat 130mph
OL,6,FShe fondly recalls her father gifting
OL,7,Fher a Wolseley Hornet sports car for
OL,8,Fher 21st birthday, which she used to
OL,9,Fdrive colleagues to and from work.
OL,11,F"The journey took us along winding,
OL,12,Fhilly country roads," she said.
OL,14,F"We used to build up speed going up a
OL,15,Fhill, switch off the engine, and then
OL,16,Fcoast down the other side to save
OL,17,Fpetrol."
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@UO]vD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
