CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782199087
OL,3,CSpeed-loving OAP races round Thruxton
OL,4,Cat 130mph
OL,6,FChris Golding, COO at The Dower House,
OL,7,Fwho attended the event, said: "We are
OL,8,Fpassionate about supporting our
OL,9,Fresidents to continue living life as
OL,10,Ffully and independently as possible.
OL,12,F"Today has been incredibly special,
OL,13,Fseeing Miss Elliott relive something
OL,14,Fshe truly loves."
OL,26,@oD@_OU
